com.aevi.printing.model

Class PrintPayload

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aevi.printing.model.PrintPayload
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class PrintPayload
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    A PrintPayload contains a collection of PrintRow that represent a printable text document.

    By binding to the PrintService this pay load can be send to the receipt printer for printing.
